<body>
    <h1>Cricket - A Popular Sport</h1>
    <p><strong>Cricket</strong> is a game played between two teams of 11 players each. It is a <u>bat-and-ball</u> sport that originated in <i>England</i>.</p>
    <p style="color: #000080;">The game is played on a <span style="font-weight: bold;">circular field</span> with a <span style="font-style: italic;">pitch</span> in the center.</p>
    <h2>Basic Rules:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>One team bats to score runs.</li>
        <li>The other team bowls and fields to restrict runs.</li>
        <li>The team with the highest runs wins!</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="color: #800000;"><strong>Fun Fact:</strong> The most popular cricket tournaments include the <span style="text-decoration: underline;">ICC World Cup</span> and the IPL.</p>
